i_{o1} - i_{o2} \approx I \times \frac{v_{x}}{2 V_{T}} \times \frac{v_{y}}{2 V_{T}} \tag{5.75}
\end{equation*}
$$

Clearly, in this mode, the cell functions as a true four-quadrant multiplier.

